strings.Value: "These barbarians make marvelous characters... All we need is some savage with a high sense of honor!"
"Do you ever talk about anything besides your book? Life is so much bigger than art can ever portray. People are so much more complicated than any sketch conveys..."
"Trust me, you don't want to know them better..."
"Take me for example! You see every day how honorable I can be. And you hear every night how savage, ha, ha, ha!"
